        <return-value transfer-ownership="full">
          <doc xml:space="preserve"
               filename="gpiod-glib/request-config.h"
               line="30">New #GpiodglibRequestConfig.

The constructor allows to set object's properties when it's first created
instead of having to build an empty object and then call mutators separately.

Currently supported properties are: `consumer` and `event-buffer-size`.</doc>
          <type name="RequestConfig" c:type="GpiodglibRequestConfig*"/>
